This webpage reproduces an English translation of the
				<B>
				<SPAN CLASS="larger">
				<BR>
Cato Maior De Senectute
				</SPAN>
				<BR>
by
				<BR>
				<SPAN CLASS="larger">
Cicero
				</SPAN>
				</B>
				<BR>
published in the
Loeb Classical Library,
				<BR>
1923
			<P CLASS="center">
The text is in the public domain.

			<P CLASS="center">
This page has been carefully proofread
