"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">5</A>
<I>Cf.</I> Plato, <I>Rep.</I> 328<SPAN CLASS="small">E</SPAN>. Cicero almost translates the words there addressed by Socrates to the aged Cephalus.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note6" HREF="
